dct_title_s: The Hannibal & St. Joseph Rail Road Co.offer for sale over 500,000 acres of prairie, timber, and coal lands in Northern Missouri
dct_description_sm: Includes "Profile of the Hannibal & St. Joseph Rail Road." "Land is sold for land bonds & preferred stock or on 10 years credit. For full particulars apply to or address Geo. S. Harris, Land Commissioner, Hannibal, Mo." Promotional text in red.
dct_publisher_sm: [Hannibal, Mo.? : s.n., ca. 1856] (Boston : A. Meisel, lith.)
dct_subject_sm: Hannibal and St. Joseph Railroad Company
dcat_theme_sm: Hannibal and St. Joseph Railroad Company
